| Metric                  | Formula                            | Value       |
| ----------------------- | ---------------------------------- | ----------- |
| **MTTD**                | Detection Time - Attack Start Time | **2 hours** |
| **MTTR**                | Response Time - Detection Time     | **4 hours** |
| **False Positive Rate** | False Alerts / Total Alerts × 100  | **15%**     |
